data.description: If you're considering an investment opportunity this multi unit is for you! This beautiful building is located in the Humboldt Park neighborhood which is known for its rich cultural diversity, green spaces, and community spirit. The first-floor unit has 2 bedrooms /1 full bathroom, while the second-floor unit has 3 bedrooms / 1 full bathroom. Additionally, there is a full-finished basement with 2 bedrooms / 1 full bathroom. The presence of multiple bedrooms and bathrooms can be attractive for potential tenants. Laundry: There is a common laundry area which is a great selling point for potential tenants. The property has a brand new detached 2-car garage, which is a valuable amenity for residents who own vehicles. New hot water heater in 2022. Location is near essential grocery stores, shopping, schools, and the 606 trail.
